name: Fallen Queen III: Grudge
description: @AledinArt | "Fallen Queen III: Grudge" is one of the 3 pieces "Fallen Queens" collection by Alejandro Dini, the other two being "Fallen Queen I: Bile" and "Fallen Queen II: Sorrow". They represent dark emotional states towering over reason, as they appear in famous ancient folk tales often embodied by witches or queens.
